'''Jamison Jones''' (born [[February 15]], [[1960s#1969|1969]]) is an actor who portrayed [[Rookie One]], the protagonist in the live action cutscenes of ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire]]''. He also had an uncredited role as "Pilot" in [[George Lucas]]' 1994 film [[Wikipedia:Radioland Murders|''Radioland Murders'']], and a part in [[Wikipedia:Hollywood Homicide|''Hollywood Homicide'']] (2003) with [[Harrison Ford]].

